# 🎥 YouTube Video Flashcard Generator

This web app lets you generate flashcards from YouTube videos by analyzing their transcripts. Perfect for students and lifelong learners who want to break down video lectures or tutorials into concise, reviewable flashcards.

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Paste a YouTube URL and generate flashcards automatically.  
✅ Uses video transcripts to extract key points.  
✅ Intuitive web UI with dark mode and modern styling.  
✅ Flashcards optimized for active recall and spaced repetition.  
✅ Built with FastAPI + EJS (or Streamlit, depending on your stack).

